  "short_description": "Do parkour with a car using explosions.🚗💥 Everything in the game is handmade from clay.🎨The sound effects and music are all mouth sounds. 👄If you screw up a jump, children laugh and make fun of you. (Just like real life!😆) Can you reach the top of the Meowtain?⛰️ Now with multiplayer!",
