et back to the previous checkpoint at anytime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582590/extras/d6d0115e50dc7aa18a930aaac032f59f.poster.avif?t=1765375090\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582590/extras/d6d0115e50dc7aa18a930aaac032f59f.webm?t=1765375090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582590/extras/d6d0115e50dc7aa18a930aaac032f59f.mp4?t=1765375090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Not an epic open world game or a live service game! Plus it's super cheap!</strong>💰☕️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game respects your time. It's a few hours long, depending on how good you are at it. You buy it, play it for a bit and have fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's less than a cup of coffee. Why is coffee so expensive anyways? Buy more indie games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582590/extras/8838f9855ce15f5724789aad8517fb2a.poster.avif?t=1765375090\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582590/extras/8838f9855ce15f5724789aad8517fb2a.webm?t=1765375090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582590/extras/8838f9855ce15f5724789aad8517fb2a.mp4?t=1765375090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deedlee Doo! Carkour!🚗💥</strong>🎸</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582590/extras/e8042a7f89bc0e48a9b71efa2fffbb5c.avif?t=1765375090\" width=615 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Deedlee Doo! Carkour!\" is developed by Nate Purkeypile. Nate Purkeypile has been making games for 21+ years and worked on titles such as Skyrim, Fallout 3/4/76, Starfield, Metroid Prime 3 and BloodRayne 2. He was the Lead Artist on Fallout 76 and the Co-Lead/Lead Artist on the Fallout 3 DLC, Point Lookout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After working in AAA games for years and years, he became a solo indie developer. His last indie game was The Axis Unseen, a heavy metal horror game where you hunt monsters from folklore. Now he made this thing. Have fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
